<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٦٦٨ - قَالَ مَعْمَرٌ ,<span class="c5"> وَقَالَ قَتَادَةُ:</span> <span class="c2">«إِلَّا الْمَيْتَةَ , وَمَا لَمْ يُذْكَرِ اسْمُ اللَّهِ عَلَيْهِ»</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>